<h2 id="the-shortcuts-class">The Shortcuts class</h2>

<p>A helper module that allow to easily set up and remove app shortcuts. Please note that keybindings should be in the form <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">[ctrl+][shift+][alt+]key</code>.</p>

<h3 id="methods">Methods</h3>

<h4 id="add"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">add</code></h4>

<p><strong>Description:</strong> Adds a new shortcut to the app.</p>

<p><strong>Arguments:</strong> <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">callback</code>,Â <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">...keybindings</code></p>

<p><strong>Return value:</strong> None</p>

<h4 id="remove"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">remove</code></h4>

<p><strong>Description:</strong> Removes the given <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">keybindings</code>.</p>

<p><strong>Arguments:</strong> <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">...keybindings</code></p>

<p><strong>Return value:</strong> None</p>
